last_episode_to_air.name: Dun Dun Done!
last_episode_to_air.overview: Lulu, Frankie and Bruce are three Aussie siblings who move with their parents to a B&B in Tubbershandy, an isolated seaside village in western Ireland. Fitting in to a new hometown is hard enough without having to hide a secret so huge as zombie parents. And the methods Lulu, Bruce and Frankie must invent on a daily (even hourly!) basis to keep the truth under wraps are a constant source of adventure and hilarity. For the Champ Clan, life in Tubbershandy can get pretty interesting - and weird.

name: Drop Dead Weird
overview: Three Australian siblings move to a bed and breakfast in Tubbershandy western Ireland with their Zombie parents.
